@baseUrl = http://localhost:5112

### Index
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Add a new book
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "title": "Dune",
  "category": "Science",
  "read": true
}

